item.title: CVE-2018-1690|2024-08-05T04:07:44.363Z -- ibm -- rhapsody%20model%20manager
item.description: IBM Rhapsody Model Manager 6.0.6 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 145510.
